@database VolumelistClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Volumelist Class"


Volumelist class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "ListClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Volumelist class is used to create a list of the available
  volumes.

  A volume list object is a LIST that can be used with Listview
  objects.

  See @{"List" LINK "ListClass.guide/Main"} @{"Listview" LINK "ListviewFunctions.guide/Main"}.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  None defined

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  @{fg shine}GetEntry@{fg text}
  <pos>,<stem>
  pos is a number or Active
  stem will contain the name of the volume in .NAME

@EndNode

